&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Home to the award winning Mafia franchise, our team are united by passion for rich narrative storytelling, cinematic presentation and AAA craft. We&#39;re looking for creative minds and driven professionals who share our love of story, style, and adventure. If you&#39;re ready to help shape the next generation of narrative driven games, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are looking for a Lead Lighting Artist to help shape and deliver world-class real-time lighting across gameplay, cinematics, and key marketing assets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role sits at the intersection of creativity and technical expertise, using Unreal Engine 5 to create lighting that enhances atmosphere, storytelling, and player experience while meeting performance goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reporting to the Art Director, the Lead Lighting Artist will work closely with Engineering, and the other Art Disciplines, playing a key role in defining lighting solutions that are both visually ambitious and technically robust.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Lighting Quality &amp;amp; Vision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and execute the lighting vision in alignment with the game’s art direction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set and maintain lighting standards and best practices to ensure a consistent, high-quality visual bar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create lighting that supports mood, composition, readability, and emotional impact across a wide range of content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gameplay, Cinematic &amp;amp; Marketing Lighting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead lighting for real-time gameplay and in-engine cinematics, ensuring a cohesive visual experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with a cross-disciplinary team on the creation of high-end marketing and promotional assets, contributing ideas and helping deliver polished, visually striking results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt lighting solutions to work effectively across gameplay and cinematics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unreal Engine 5 Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a go-to expert for UE5 lighting, with hands-on experience using systems such as Lumen, Virtual Shadow Maps, exposure, and post-processing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use UE5’s lighting capabilities to push visual quality while maintaining performance and stability.&lt;/li&gt;
