&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work within Unreal Engine 5, adapting existing animation systems and building new technology to meet the project&#39;s technical and creative needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prototype and implement animation features and runtime systems (animation graphs, state machines, blending, layering).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain animation tools and pipelines that empower animators and technical artists to work efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely and constructively with animation, art, design, and engineering teams to realise creative ambitions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support planning efforts by estimating and dependency-checking animation feature development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify technical and developmental risks/obstacles and generate solutions to overcome them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research coding techniques and algorithms to stay current with technological developments and advancements in animation and the wider game industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
